description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applications are invited for a Consultant Medical Oncologist specialising in Gynaecological and Urological cancers at Portsmouth Oncology Centre, Hampshire.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Portsmouth Hospitals University Trust, based at Queen Alexandra Hospital has a vision to be recognized as a world-class hospital, leading the field through innovative healthcare solutions, focusing on the best outcomes for our patients, delivered in a safe, caring and inspiring environment. Portsmouth Cancer Centre also provides cancer services to West Sussex (Chichester) and the Isle of Wight. We are a friendly and integrated Centre embracing enhanced radiographer, nursing and pharmacy roles, and actively encouraging research and innovation. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The area combines the advantages of city life with rural villages and seaside towns. Portsmouth is a thriving naval city, steeped in history, on the beautiful South Coast. It is ninety minutes from central London and has good transport links by ferry and airplane into Europe. Water sports facilities are excellent with access to the Solent and sandy beaches are within easy reach. Inland is the spectacular and relatively unspoilt countryside of rural Hampshire, and the South Downs National Park. It is an excellent place to raise a family.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a 10 PA post, but applicants wishing to work less than full time are most welcome to discuss their requirements, and indeed other sub-specialty interests could be accommodated. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please contact Dr Caroline Archer, Clinical Director, &lt;span&gt;caroline.archer@porthosp.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt; - phone 02392286000 ext 4790 for informal discussion and further information&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: &lt;/strong&gt;Sunday 8th November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview date: &lt;/strong&gt;To be confirmed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
